textAfterTable: Event Detail Information Event Detail Information A Conversation with the ECE Department Head Speaker Andreas Cangellaris, M.E. Van Valkenburg Professor of ECE and Department Head Date Oct 10, 2012 Time 5:00 pm   Location 151 Everitt Lab Sponsor ECE Explorations Seminar Event type Academic Views 2188 Originating Calendar CSL General Event Calendar Join ECE Department Head Andreas Cangellaris for a dialog on what you like about your experiences in our Department and the College, what you don't like, why you don't like it, and your thoughts on how it could be changed for the better. Andreas Cangellaris is the M. E. Van Valkenburg Professor of ECE. His research interests include electromagnetic field theory, electromagnetic device/circuit computer-aided design, RF/microwave engineering, and noise-aware design of high-speed/high-frequency electronic systems. Open to all | Pizza will be provided after the talk! link for robots
